{"tid":834950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(神預言) 下個月有新沙士","createTime":"2018-09-24T13:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T12:54:14.000Z","uid":44711,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d601e6b85fe641caec7c3924033afef24a446806","tid":834950,"uid":44711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"十月份起即將開始有一長期的病毒病菌的傳染感染的狀況．大家要更注意衛生與飲食的新鮮度，空氣的污染與水質的污染也將是傳染的途徑之一．任何可能性的傳染途徑都要注意，例如，急性拉肚子，噁心嘔吐與肺炎，腸胃不舒服與腸病毒，咳嗽不止．皮膚紅疹出問題與血液異常，感冒狀況等等的現象，ㄧ定要即刻就醫，並且要快速殺菌，不能讓病毒在體內超過七天．否則會有異常的併發症與敗血症的產生．<br />\n<br />\n全世界<br />\n傳染力死亡率潛伏期up"},{"pid":"5599b314f2aea24c5a1297b420b6295933cf0f60","tid":834950,"uid":52571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"有咩留返同個官講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ba38b630d715d540c72d166249292e85a065d0","tid":834950,"uid":117407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我突然有紅疹，全身勁痕<br />\n樓主係先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88fd5e0ba57eaa33ae7f6dd34ae4b1d75e3fc5b","tid":834950,"uid":44711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4ba38b630d715d540c72d166249292e85a065d0","tid":834950,"uid":117407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我突然有紅疹，全身勁痕<br />\n樓主係先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"屌我都係，認真，我以為比野咬。換撚哂啲床單都仲係咁"},{"pid":"9476c028f684f3cbaea943ea27